description:
What to Know before You Go

Travel Documentary hosted by Josh Gates, published by Travel Channel UK broadcasted as part of Expedition Unknown Series 2 Special series in 2016 - English narration 
http://docuwiki.net/images/4/47/What-to-Know-before-You-Go-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------

Expedition Unknown Series 2 Special: What To Know Before You Go
Inspired by his adventures while filming Expedition Unknown, Josh shares tips on the best way to travel in this special episode. Josh also features bonus scenes and hilarious outtakes from some of his recent expeditions.
